---
title: Sticky Chicken & Roast Veggie Salad with Creamy Pesto Dressing & Almonds
description: A little salty and squeaky, with a touch of tang, we're big chicken fans - especially when it's teamed with sweet roasted veggies. Dress the salad with creamy pesto dressing and top with crunchy almonds for the best balance of flavours and textures. Don't forget the herb garnish, it really makes everything sing!
